text: Celeste Maloy (born May 22, 1981) is an American politician and lawyer who is the U.S. representative for since 2023. She is a member of the Republican Party. She was the chief legal counsel to U.S. Representative Chris Stewart. Maloy worked as a conservationist for the Natural Resources Conservation Service. ==References== ==Other websites== * Congresswoman Celeste Maloy official U.S. House website * Celeste Maloy for Congress campaign website * * * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from Utah Category:Lawyers from Utah Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
